- This means..<br>
- No! No science camp!
<SYNC Start=1320880><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1321053><P Class=ENCC>
Damn it! I'll put a candle on the cake.
<SYNC Start=1325649><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1325824><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, and, Emma, look at your<br>
