<SYNC Start=1331694><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1331963><P Class=ENCC>
Thanks.
<SYNC Start=1333828><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1333999><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, here we go.
<SYNC Start=1337264><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1337636><P Class=ENCC>
Emma's first birthday cake.
<SYNC Start=1341970><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1342841><P Class=ENCC>
Go ahead, Emma,<br>
blow out the candle.
<SYNC Start=1344638><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1344810><P Class=ENCC>
Come on, Emma. You can do it.
<SYNC Start=1347404><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1347579><P Class=ENCC>
- What's wrong? Are you okay?<br>
- Oh, yeah, nothing.
<SYNC Start=1350673><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1350849><P Class=ENCC>
These are happy tears.
<SYNC Start=1353409><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1353585><P Class=ENCC>
This is just what I wanted.
<SYNC Start=1355883><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1357622><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, you made it into a bunny.
<SYNC Start=1359351><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1361493><P Class=ENCC>
What is wrong with me? It looked<br>
more delicious when it was a penis.
<SYNC Start=1364951><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1370268><P Class=ENCC>
- Okay, you ready?<br>
- Yeah.
<SYNC Start=1371929><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
