I'm kind of a player.
<SYNC Start=1379800><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1379978><P Class=ENCC>
Okay. Let's..
<SYNC Start=1381969><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1382748><P Class=ENCC>
- Let's just try that again.<br>
- Okay.
<SYNC Start=1385842><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1387419><P Class=ENCC>
Hi, Emma.<br>
Well, your first birthday is over, and..
<SYNC Start=1391788><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
